  <prompt>
    Per FR-15, document the JSON envelope schema in `notes/insight-envelope-schema.md` with extraction examples for downstream consumers (Power Fx for canvas apps, plugin/C# for server-side, view/column transformation for reports). This unblocks downstream teams to consume `.body` plaintext from the envelope.
  </prompt>

  <role>Technical documentation author.</role>

  <goal>
    `notes/insight-envelope-schema.md` containing: full schema definition (JSON Schema), narrative description of each field, 3 extraction examples (Power Fx, plugin C#, view column).
  </goal>

  <inputs>
    <file purpose="spec">projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-widgets-r1/spec.md (FR-14, FR-15)</file>
  </inputs>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec-FR-15">3 extraction examples minimum (Power Fx, plugin, view/column)</constraint>
    <constraint source="Q-U1">schemaVersion type = string ("1.0")</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <topic>json schema, power fx, dataverse plugin, downstream consumer patterns</topic>
    <files>
      <file>projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-widgets-r1/spec.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1" name="Compose JSON Schema definition">Match FR-14 envelope shape; schemaVersion: string</step>
    <step order="2" name="Write Power Fx example">JSON parse + .body extract for canvas app</step>
    <step order="3" name="Write plugin C# example">Newtonsoft.Json.Linq.JObject parse</step>
    <step order="4" name="Write view/column example">Plain Text Annotation for column transformation</step>
    <step order="5" name="Cross-link from spec.md FR-15">Update spec reference</step>
  </steps>

  <outputs>
    <output type="notes">projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-widgets-r1/notes/insight-envelope-schema.md</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
